<br>
Total: 17<br>
<br>
Relics:<br>
<br>
1x <a href="javascript:card_browser(488)">Digging Goggles</a><br>
1x <a href="javascript:card_browser(644)">Tunneler&#39;s Boots</a><br>
2x <a href="javascript:card_browser(512)">Warrior&#39;s Boots</a><br>
2x <a href="javascript:card_browser(507)">Relic Stalker</a><br>
1x <a href="javascript:card_browser(789)">Tomorrow&#39;s Jewel</a><br>
2x <a href="javascript:card_browser(652)">Rayje&#39;s Belt</a><br>
